description: [``botocore``] This release adds support to customize prompts sent through the RetrieveAndGenerate API in Agents for Amazon Bedrock.
[``botocore``] Adds support for backfill of cost allocation tags, with new StartCostAllocationTagBackfill and ListCostAllocationTagBackfillHistory API.
[``botocore``] Documentation updates for Elastic Compute Cloud (EC2).
[``botocore``] This is a documentation update for Amazon ECS.
[``botocore``] Add new operation delete-kx-cluster-node and add status parameter to list-kx-cluster-node operation.
